== Welcome to Rails
1. how to run it 
   you should setup one local database named lbscdevelopment under mysql
2. download the source code from 
   http://github.com/cuinate/LBSC/archives/master
   unzip it and enter the folder in shell or CMD
   run following :
   rake db:migrate
   if ok , then 
   ruby script/server 
3. using your browser , enter http://localhost:3000.

that's all!